Terry McCarty was just six years old when he suffered third-degree burns to 70 per cent of his body in a childhood accident . 
  He endured 58 operations and cruel taunts from bullies who called him Freddy Krueger because of the scars . 
  The 29-year-old from Nevada has now become a firefighter . 
  He was engulfed with flames after his brothers filled a bowl with kerosene which was accidentally knocked on to him . 
 